labels.name: P2: Fix can wait a while

data.actual_result: The user talking back sounds a little static. It’s noticeable only for the user who watched a video
data.expected_result: Normal voice like before watching a video
data.steps_to_repro: - Launch Discord and get into a voice channel - When in voice play a youtube video in any discord chat. This can be paused after a second or so - let the user talk to you again and you will hear a static noice
